name: Time Force
details:
Digital delay with 11 models, tap tempo, presets and a 45 sec looperCheap digital delay pedal with good sound and lots of options.
Possibility of stereo in/out, 11 delay models, tap tempo with subdivisions, 9 presets to store settings, 45 second looper, buffered or true bypass, option to use delay trails to go after it's turned off, possibility of wet only signal.
